{"tid":381760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣手機殼任拎　途人蜂擁搶貨","createTime":"2017-08-31T08:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T03:53:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a23917c6ee03c6c5f2d6173730a517a8a40773c2","tid":381760,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=0f166544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001_06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001_06p.jpg&h=6b77088d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地上執到寶，問天問地攞唔到！有網民今早(31日)在銅鑼灣發現，大量全新手機殼被棄置街頭，一眾路經的途人即上前尋寶，人揀你又揀，個個執到四萬咁口，睇嚟真筍貨喎！<br />\n<br />\n網民Waly Lee在Facebook「香港突發事故報料區」上載照片，指早上11時半，行經銅鑼灣利園山道及白沙道，發現街道上有數箱紙皮箱，上前打開一看，發現紙箱內都是全新手機殼，亦有不同型號，有市民看見後便蜂擁而至，不少市民收穫豐富。<br />\n<br />\n圖片上載後，有網民欣喜若狂，留言<span style=\"color: red;\">「飛緊的黎(嚟)攞，知唔知仲有無？」，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「咁筍執到個ip(iPhone)殼，那那(嗱嗱)林去買部ip(iPhone)先」</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過，亦有網民認為，若不適合，即使免費亦無用。<br />\n<br />\n東網記者下午1時許到達現場，發現只剩下少量手機殼及零件，而手機殼大部分都是較舊的型號，如iPhone 5、Sony等，現場留下大量包裝，尤如垃圾堆。記者在現場觀察，發現已沒有瘋狂搶殼的情況，只是偶然有一至兩位途人撿起手機殼。記者問及途人為何取走非自己手機型號的手機殼，途人表示「是但攞」；記者又問是否因為看見Facebook貼文才過來，他表示「唔知你講咩」。<br />\n<br />\n有附近店舖不願透姓名的女職員表示，今早10時許已發現該處有10多箱包裝好的紙箱，當時未有為意，其後愈來愈多途人圍着紙箱，她始知有手機殼執。她指高峰期有10多人一起執筍貨。另外一位不願上鏡的手機店職員表示，該是樓上舖的手機店結業，將貨尾放在該址。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nCarol Ca：可能係d(啲)好舊款，以前都有人掉出街，送俾(畀)你都冇(無)用<br />\n<br />\nHarold Poon：放箱野(嘢)，set個cam，可能係社會實驗<br />\n<br />\nNick Leung：會唔會有人唔見左(咗)一箱貨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/bkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170831%2Fbkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001.html&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d413c1b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170831/bkn-20170831121344370-0831_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ebaf58adb233e99cea4ebf1fabf3aefce09d1c40","tid":381760,"uid":41818,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"00097ffcdfc513910670f2167c187fd6e4230ac1","tid":381760,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"a56e28a17195c862153b5a48a9cd81785e8a546e","tid":381760,"uid":54927,"like":290,"dislike":3,"score":287,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"香港人啲舉動同中國人真係好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9351d5a041ff1b2bd536fef2c999e39271324b8","tid":381760,"uid":8681,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人啲舉動同中國人真係好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不用分得那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2bad03eed6336155fc7c39e856005aa2cad2cc","tid":381760,"uid":90863,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"中國人本性盡現"},{"pid":"bd964d7ca6edb96b9f716f1efa95d750c920af58","tid":381760,"uid":98386,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:27:13.000Z","msg":"班連登仔成日笑尻支那人 自以為港柒高人一等 而家就足以證明港柒好唔得過支那人好多"},{"pid":"505c29c45d48a3cbf696fc746149b6df4bebea15","tid":381760,"uid":59886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"張圖好嘈"},{"pid":"181f22aa47682b0cd4968cda42de9b18725faa8e","tid":381760,"uid":63057,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"r